                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He also</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">to a previous conviction at Newington in September</hi>, 1876—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18791020-985-punishment-82" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18791020-985-punishment-82" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
